    {
      "text": "Kowai Shashin is a horror game released for the Sony Playstation in 2002, it is vagyuely similar to the Fatal Frame series.\nGameplay consists of finding a spirit in a creepy photograph, and catching it trough a quick time event.\nThere´s an urban legend around the game, considering it a cursed one, because of supposed deaths and hauntings during the development (which isn't true, at least, no one died during the making of the game).",
